const projectsData = [
  {
    id: 1,
    title: "Aurum Finance Platform",
    description: "A premium fintech experience translating complex data into crystal-clear decisions.",
    techStack: ["React", "TypeScript", "Node.js", "PostgreSQL"],
    imageLabel: "Fintech Dashboard",
    overview: "A high-trust platform for private wealth clients, designed to make portfolio performance feel effortless.",
    problem: "Legacy dashboards overwhelmed clients with dense tables and unclear hierarchy, reducing confidence.",
    solution: "Designed a narrative-first dashboard with modular insights, subtle motion, and a refined visual system.",

  {
    id: 2,
    title: "Noir Commerce Suite",
    description: "A luxury e-commerce toolkit optimized for speed, elegance, and conversion.",

    imageLabel: "Luxury Commerce",
    overview: "A composable storefront platform that balances performance engineering with cinematic product storytelling.",
    problem: "High-end retailers struggled to maintain brand prestige while meeting modern performance needs.",
    solution: "Built a modular system with bespoke product narratives, instant loading, and refined micro-interactions.",
    visuals: ["Concept Boards", "Component Library", "Launch Page"]
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    title: "Echelon Health Studio",
    description: "A digital care experience unifying patient clarity and operational excellence.",
    techStack: ["React", "Node.js", "GraphQL", "Figma"],
    imageLabel: "Health Experience",
    overview: "An end-to-end patient portal and clinician dashboard built for clarity, empathy, and speed.",
    problem: "Patients felt disconnected while clinicians battled fragmented workflows.",
    solution: "Designed a unified journey across patient and clinician touchpoints with seamless data flow.",
    visuals: ["Journey Map", "Prototype", "Final UI"]
  }
];
